yhadithonline\/2013\/01\/15\/lesser-greater-jihad-al-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":26091,"position":0},"title":"Ibrahim on Jihad: Greater Jihad is struggle to purify the heart","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 15, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Ibrahim ibn Abi 'Alqamah, may Allah have mercy on him, said to his people when they returned from a military expedition, \u201cYou have come from the lesser jihad, but you have not performed the greater jihad.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat is the greater jihad?\u201d Ibrahim said, \u201cIt is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8000,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/13\/mujahid-jihad-against-his-soul\/","url_meta":{"origin":26091,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Jihad: True Mujahid fights jihad against his own soul","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn 'Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe one who strives in jihad is the one who strives against himself.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1621 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u062c\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u062f\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26713,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/09\/jihad-greatest-enemy-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":26091,"position":2},"title":"Hasan on Jihad: Your greatest enemy is your own ego","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 9, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Tabari reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYour enemy is not the one you are relieved from if you killed him. Rather, your true enemy is your own soul, between your two sides.\u201d Al-Tabari said, \u201cIt is the jihad against the greatest of enemies to a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26779,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/08\/27\/sufyan-greatest-jihad-nafs\/","url_meta":{"origin":26091,"position":3},"title":"Sufyan on Nafs: Hardest struggle was against my own self","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 27, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Waki\u2019 reported: Sufyan al-Thawri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI never dealt with anything more difficult on me than my own self. Sometimes it would be against me, and sometimes it would be for me.\u201d Source: H\u0323ilyat al-Awliya\u0304\u2019 7\/5 \u0639\u0646 \u0648\u0643\u064a\u0639 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u06